.TH FRESHER 1 "2026-05-31" "fresher 0.3.10" "Fresher Editor"
.SH NAME
fresher \- terminal text editor with LSP and TypeScript plugins
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B fresher
[\fIOPTIONS\fR]
[\fIFILES\fR...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B fresher
is a lightweight terminal-based text editor with LSP support, syntax
highlighting, multi-cursor editing, and a TypeScript plugin runtime.
.PP
File arguments accept several syntaxes:
.IP \(bu 2
\fIfile\fR \(em open a file
.IP \(bu 2
\fIfile\fR:\fIline\fR[:\fIcol\fR] \(em open a file and jump to a position
.IP \(bu 2
\fIfile\fR:\fIline\fR:\fIcol\fR\-\fIline\fR:\fIcol\fR \(em open a file with a selection range
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-a ", " \-\-attach " [\fINAME\fR]"
Attach to a running session. Use
.B \-a
on its own for the current directory or
.BI \-a " NAME"
for a named session.
.TP
.B \-\-stdin
Read content from standard input (alternative to passing "\-" as a filename).
.TP
.BI \-\-cmd " COMMAND..."
Run a command instead of opening files. Available commands include
.BR session " (" list ", " attach ", " new ", " kill ", " open\-file ")"
.BR config " (" show ", " paths ")"
.BR "grammar list" ,
and
.BR init .
.TP
.BI \-\-config " PATH"
Path to a configuration file.
.TP
.BI \-\-log\-file " PATH"
Path to a log file for editor diagnostics.
.TP
.BI \-\-event\-log " FILE"
Enable event logging to the specified file.
.TP
.B \-\-no\-plugins
Disable plugin loading for this launch.
.TP
.B \-\-no\-init
Skip
.I ~/.config/fresher/init.ts
for this launch.
.TP
.B \-\-safe
Safe mode: skip
.I init.ts
and all plugins (for recovering from a bad config).
.TP
.B \-\-no\-restore
Do not restore the previous workspace.
.TP
.B \-\-restore
Force restore of the previous workspace, overriding the
.B editor.restore_previous_session
configuration setting.
.TP
.B \-\-no\-upgrade\-check
Disable upgrade checking and anonymous telemetry.
.TP
.BI \-\-locale " LOCALE"
Override the interface locale (e.g.\&
.IR en ,
.IR ja ,
.IR zh\-CN ).
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Print help text.
.TP
.BR \-V ", " \-\-version
Print version information.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/fresher/config.json
Per-user editor configuration.
.TP
.I ~/.config/fresher/init.ts
Per-user initialization script, run at startup unless
.B \-\-no\-init
or
.B \-\-safe
is given.
.TP
.I ~/.config/fresher/plugins/
User-installed plugins.
.TP
.I ~/.config/fresher/themes/
User-installed themes.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/fresher/embedded\-plugins/
Cache directory for the plugin bundle compiled into the binary.
.SH SEE ALSO
Project documentation:
.UR https://nicolaslima.github.io/fresher/
.UE
.SH BUGS
Report issues at
.UR https://github.com/nicolaslima/fresher/issues
.UE .
